ZH: 勿忘初心，方得始终。
EN: Do not forget your original intention, and you will succeed in the end.

ZH: 勿近火源以免发生危险。
EN: Do not approach the source of fire to avoid danger.

ZH: 勿以善小而不为。
EN: Do not despise doing good because it is small.

ZH: 勿忘珍惜身边的人。
EN: Do not forget to cherish the people around you.

ZH: 勿因小失大。
EN: Do not lose sight of the bigger picture because of minor details.

ZH: 勿轻易相信别人的话。
EN: Do not easily trust what others say.

ZH: 勿用毒药来解决问题。
EN: Do not use poison to solve problems.

ZH: 勿动不动就发脾气。
EN: Do not get angry easily.

ZH: 勿以貌取人，内在更重要。
EN: Do not judge people by their appearance, inner qualities are more important.

ZH: 勿以私欲蒙蔽眼睛。
EN: Do not let selfish desires blind your eyes.

ZH: 勿过分自负，谦虚为上。
EN: Do not be overly arrogant, humility is key.

ZH: 勿忘初衷，始终如一。
EN: Do not forget your original intention, remain consistent.

ZH: 勿过度依赖他人。
EN: Do not overly rely on others.

ZH: 勿让失败打败你的信心。
EN: Do not let failure defeat your confidence.

ZH: 勿被困难吓倒，勇往直前。
EN: Do not be intimidated by difficulties, move forward bravely.

ZH: 勿小看自己的价值和潜力。
EN: Do not underestimate your own value and potential.

ZH: 勿让负面情绪影响你的决策。
EN: Do not let negative emotions influence your decision-making.

ZH: 勿忘感恩之心。
EN: Do not forget to be grateful.

ZH: 勿利用他人手段来实现个人目的。
EN: Do not use others as a means to achieve personal goals.

ZH: 勿盲目追求物质享受。
EN: Do not blindly pursue material pleasures.
